name: DA Stores
overview:
Since 2006, DA Stores LLC has offered the highest quality furniture and the widest selection available anywhere. We are a Los Angeles, CA based company with a passion for home furnishings. We take our responsibility to our customers seriously. Our group of buyers scours the world over to find the latest in design trends, the finest materials and the most cost-effective way to get these furnishings to our loyal customers. With a group of the most knowledgeable customer service reps who stand ready to answer any questions or provide assistance, we’re sure we have the ideal combination of excellent service and quality furniture offerings.

Simply put, our goal and mission is to ensure every customer who visit our sites comes away satisfied with their purchase and with the knowledge they’re important to our company. With easy to browse sites that are transparent in their pricing and shipping guidelines, we know you’ll be convinced too. Along with an extensive selection of the finest furniture, you’ll find a wide array of accessories, lighting options, outdoor products and don’t forget our beautiful imported rugs.
